<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Acesso Negado</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: #00bd10;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #007906;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Acesso Negado</h1>
        <p>Você não está logado. Por favor, faça login para continuar.</p>
        <a href="/login" class="btn">Ir para Login</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
